raw_meta_yaml:
context:
  version: 5.4.1
  python_min: "3.7"

package:
  name: flask-socketio
  version: ${{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/f/flask-socketio/flask_socketio-${{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 2e9b8864a5be37ca54f6c76a4d06b1ac5e0df61fde12d03afc81ab4057e1eb86

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: python -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - python ${{ python_min }}
    - pip
    - setuptools >=61.2
  run:
    - python >=${{ python_min }}
    - flask >=0.9
    - python-socketio >=5.0.2

tests:
  - python:
      imports:
        - flask_socketio
        - flask_socketio.namespace
        - flask_socketio.test_client
  - script:
      - python -c "import flask_socketio"
    requirements:
      run:
        - python ${{ python_min }}

about:
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Socket.IO integration for Flask applications
  homepage: https://github.com/miguelgrinberg/Flask-SocketIO/
  repository: https://github.com/miguelgrinberg/Flask-SocketIO/
  documentation: https://flask-socketio.readthedocs.io/en/latest/

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - pmlandwehr
    - synapticarbors
